<html t:type="layout" title="Privacy Policy"
      xmlns:t="http://tapestry.apache.org/schema/tapestry_5_4.xsd"
        >
<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<div class="bg-success">
    <p>This site uses cookies to maintain session state. Access to the site is logged. This logging includes IP, time, URL, and user agent. As this site uses
        federated login, username information from third parties is also stored when a user logs in. There are no passwords stored for the system.</p>
    <p>The core of the site is in collecting capstone exchange proposal information. That information is used as follows:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Country, Institution, and Department as well as Sponsoring Company Name and Country information will be made public so people can see who is involved.</li>
        <li>Data associated with a project request, name, phone number and email address will be shared with the paired university so they know how to contact each other and what the paired university requested.</li>
        <li>Company name and country may be made public and other associated company information will be shared between paired universities.</li>
        <li>System messages and updates will be sent to your email address.</li>
        <li>All other data will be used to administer the system by the administrators.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>If someone wants to no longer be a member, their personal data will be anonymized.</p>
    <p>If you have any questions about this policy, please <t:pagelink class="text-success" page="contact">contact us</t:pagelink>.</p>
</div>
</html>